The concept is okay, DoD camouflage device that was uncontrollably succesful. But what I really like is the ingenious transport containment procedures. It changes to something other than what you think it is, so make sure everybody thinks it is dangerous and uncontainable. There's no way to know what form it will take, but it will be by definition something containable.

